{"tid":298113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過睇中醫成功治療粉瘤?","createTime":"2017-06-26T04:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T15:22:44.000Z","uid":125148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6724aeebb7fb893ce60aed2f4b444dd8fceded7e","tid":298113,"uid":125148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"年幾前臉上開始生左粒暗瘡咁既野 一開始吱完 過一排又有過濃 不停loop<br />\n之後試去睇西醫 用左一排抗生素+消炎藥都冇用 西醫就話可能係粉瘤 如果係都只能割左去 不過留既疤可能仲難睇過粒瘤...<br />\n之後開始睇中醫 一開始個個都清得走 但結果都係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左咁耐都仲係到 變到現出粒黑頭咁既野出黎<br />\n<br />\n始終都係唔想開刀割 有冇人試過睇中醫成功清到粉瘤架??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff8bfc6c662f5e8efd32d390f41e96aa9737b95","tid":298113,"uid":125148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:44:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980dcf37efe57eaee3af3a15365f7e5b68d67dea","tid":298113,"uid":125148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c7f88b0f4fd106dbeab55f8064892906bcf3e3","tid":298113,"uid":125148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:54:25.000Z","msg":"一開始個個都<span style=\"color: red;\">話</span>清得走 <br />\n<br />\n打錯 Sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d189ea354008dd026bf31380a566424300fe4031","tid":298113,"uid":125148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017